Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:11.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我们所能驯服的严寒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This cold isn't something we can tame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我们让我们的气候成了这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We did this to our climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:21.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有地球本身能重启她温暖的心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now only the Earth herself can restart her warm heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我们能再次找到她的脉搏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe we can find her pulse again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,我最害怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And my biggest fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:33.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是死在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}isn't dying out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:37.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,而是我们中的冷血之人会在我还没证明希望前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's that the cold-hearted among us will crush that hope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,就将其浇灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,淡定  淡定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷斯劳尔研究站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Breslauer Research Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:57.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,温度为零下122.6度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The temperature is minus 122.6 Celcius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在海拔3400米上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm 11,000 feet above sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,岌岌可危\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}dangling from a thin umbilical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,距离雪国列车很遥远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Many miles from Snowpiercer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,1034节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}1,034 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.39,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs36\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,85)}雪国列{\fsp0}车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.39,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs24\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,166)}{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}第二季 第六{\fsp0}集\N{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}"远离雪国列车{\fsp0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  你在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mommy? Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我床下有怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a monster under my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:25.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:29.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are you? Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  有怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mommy, there's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了两具在大冰封时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found the bodies of two of the scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,驻扎此地的科学家的尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}stationed here at the Freeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个男性  头部中弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one male, shot in the head...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,另一个为女性  割腕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the other a woman who slit her wrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:28.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,面对世界末日这里一定是个可怕的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Must've been a grim place to face the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,但天一亮  我就得恢复这里的电力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But at first light, I have to power it back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,把我的电池加入太阳能电池阵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}patch my batteries into the solar array.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then I'll go back down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,找我的雪橇和食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for the sled I left behind with my rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:26.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,在过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the old time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,未来似乎有多个层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the future seemed multifaceted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:34.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有事业  家庭  个人抱负\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We had careers, families, personal aspirations,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:37.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,有想去的地方  想见的朋友  遗愿清单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}places to go, friends to see, bucket lists--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为理所当然的人类梦想的嗡嗡声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the hum of human dreams we took for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们其实是在梦游\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we were sleepwalking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,距离把这些所有可能的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just one step away from trading all those possible futures
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:51.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,换成大冰封的共同命运只有一步之遥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for the shared fate of the Freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought I'd find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:58.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们创造的这东西真美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a beautiful thing we've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,这要看我们如何定义"创造"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Depends how we define "Created."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你或许值得一点肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I suppose you might deserve a little credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是胶水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're the glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你把雪国列车的所有部件拼凑到了一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You put all Snowpiercer's pieces together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:17.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,她属于我也属于你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's just as much yours as she is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,你绝不会听到我当众说出这话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you will never hear me repeat that in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的投资者想听什么你就说什么  约瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever your investors need to hear, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们听到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, they heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的永动机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My "Engine Eternal."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,这要看我们如何定义"永动"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Depends how we define "Eternal."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,别毁了这一刻的气氛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}let's not ruin the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:39.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's not possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们终于能驱动她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we finally get to drive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  食物在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mommy? Where's the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去商店了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you go to the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,原来那条手臂在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, so that's where that arm went.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你疲惫不堪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是山上稀薄的空气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or is it this thin mountain air
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:07.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,让你的大脑出现了幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's playing tricks on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的供给都被雪崩埋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, with your supplies under that avalanche,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你只剩下一袋口粮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all you have left is one ration pack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,一包本给你的糖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one bag of sweeties from Ben...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,和一条手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要那条手臂也能应付过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll manage without the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:28.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  那似乎有点乐观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really? That seems a bit optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,根据日志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}According to the logbooks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,外面那些年轻的食人族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}our fine young cannibals out there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,是气候科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}were climate scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在大冰封刚开始时出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They came out at the start of the Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:44.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,寻找在CW7中存活下来的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}looking for a way to survive CW-7--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  是在其影响下存活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}well, the effects of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,显然他们没成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Apparently they didn't succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过她倒是撑了五个月之久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}though she did hang on for five months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:56.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要撑一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I only have to make it one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:56.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}30天后  雪国列车返回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,不敢看你前任们的容貌吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Afraid to look upon your predecessors' visage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想看见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just don't want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们生前有个小女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because they had a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你变得...多愁善感了  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've acquired a... sentimental streak, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:57.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你天真  有雄心壮志时更有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a lot more useful when you're naive and ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车现在应该\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer should be releasing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,正在发射第一批气象气球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the first of her weather balloons right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,给气候模拟程序打补丁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}patched into the climate-modeling program.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,只需从天线电塔连上气球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just need to link to the balloon from the radio tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,给它提供足够的数据点来推断出一个模型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Feed it enough data points to extrapolate a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,要说有谁能拼凑出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, if anyone can kludge together
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:24.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个试验性的气候模型  那一定是你  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a heuristic climate model, it's you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过可惜你得依靠本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shame you have to rely on Ben, though, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,和他的气球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And his balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有那个西班牙佬  拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that Spaniard. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你明知道哈维是哥伦比亚人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know Javi's Colombian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:38.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许你会在那里找到我们传说中的伊甸园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, well, perhaps that's where you'll find our fabled Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,他事前不知道我们要偷走你的火车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he didn't know we were stealing the train from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  我们行驶了两天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Actually, we were two days down the track
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,他才发觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before he figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,这很不错  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,辩论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jousting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,能让你忘记饥饿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keeps your mind off the hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:33.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:37.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}第一次联系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来到伊甸园还长路漫漫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Seems a long way to Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,算是个开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,饼干丢了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lost your biscuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定是吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I must've eaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没吃饼干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't eat that cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么问题来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which begs the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许我们的食人族饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps our cannibals are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,要不就是你在失去心智  工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Either that, or you're cracking up, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你不会真的要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell me you aren't really doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:44.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要这么多东西  你却在打造你的妓院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With everything else we need, you're working on your brothel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是妓院  一辆夜车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a brothel. A Nightcar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:50.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,这趟列车现在是拯救人类的方舟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This train is now an ark for humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是满足你个人的奢愿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not your personal indulgences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,不能一举两得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't it be both?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,台上艺术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Art onstage...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,后方娱乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and entertainment in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,这能让灵魂延续  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It sustains the soul, Melanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且这是个放气阀  能管住大家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it's a release valve to keep everyone under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:09.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,你浪费在这上面的资源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The resources that you're wasting on this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:12.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,能够喂饱二十人  而我们需要这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}could sustain 20 more people that we're going to need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,票务部说你从乘客名单中删掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ticketing says you removed half of my geneticists
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:17.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一半的遗传学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from the passenger list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:20.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们还有更重要的事要优先考虑  -比如呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We have more important priorities. - Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:23.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,比如你的安保吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like...your security?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证  所有枪支都会被没收\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I promised you-- all guns will be confiscated
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,从列车上扔出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and thrown from the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,但守卫能保持秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But the Jackboots will keep order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:34.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,三千个人挤在16公里长的钢管里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}3,000 souls stuffed into a 10-mile steel tube--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会突然之间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you think they're all gonna suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,和谐相处吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}start singing "Kumbaya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得如果我们要拯救人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think that if we are going to save humankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:46.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要真正知道如何拯救人类的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we need people who actually know how to save humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,-要多少  -六个遗传学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How many? - Six geneticists...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,和他们的亲属  一共12人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and next of kin--12 total.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,-去掉12个守卫  -我去掉六个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Just cut 12 Jackboots. - I'll cut six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,约瑟夫  拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Joseph, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有比秩序更重要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are gonna be more important things than order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么比秩序更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing's more important than order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真的相信自己说的鬼话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you even believe in any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,显然我让你工作太辛苦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clearly, I've been working you too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:19.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我原谅你刚才说的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which is why I will forgive what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:24.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车只有一位首席工程师  她的创造者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer has only one Head Engineer--her creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:26.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,她听我的命令运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She runs on my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:29.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你无法接受这点  那么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if you can't accept that, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的家人可以不用上车了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}your family can stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:34.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,听明白了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你没法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你没法粉饰世界末日  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you can't sugarcoat the end of the world, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:41.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是一切都会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not everything's going to be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I promise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  约瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我来到这已经十天了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been ten days since I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有食物的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I had food...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,这会是一个光鲜亮丽的报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This would be a glowing report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,每一次新的探测  系统就会收集更多的数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With each new probe, the system has more data,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我逐渐搭建出一个气候模型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I coax a climate model.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,"画作"还远未完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The picture's far from complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在问题是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:31.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是否能活着完成它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is whether I can survive long enough to finish painting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,饥饿很难受吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hunger's a bitch, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,你稍微感受到了一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're getting a little taste
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,你对我们在车尾做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of what you did to us back in the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:06.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要戳痛处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not to rub it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  你就是在戳我痛处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you're rubbing it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:10.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,那些尸体可能有点冻伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Those bodies might have a little freezer burn,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是最好不要介意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I wouldn't let that put you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不做评价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No judgment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会诉诸于食人肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not resorting to cannibalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你试试没有食物再过一个周再说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give yourself another week with no food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这很疯狂  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know this is crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:28.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经过去七年了  怎么会有东西还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been seven years. How could anything be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:30.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,是不该有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  要么是外面确实有什么东西存活了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So either something did survive out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,是个奇迹  要么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which is a miracle, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:37.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm losing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你说的  我可没说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You said it, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:50.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh! Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,看上去像是个车尾人会设计出的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Looks like something a Tailie would've cooked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:17.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想我发现的那三具尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been thinking about the three bodies I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:18.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,风流韵事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Torrid affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,亚瑟是第一个去世的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Arthur was the first to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:23.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是那个头盖骨中了一枪的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The fellow with the bullet in his brainpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,另两个人除掉了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The other two got rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,-他是她的丈夫  -真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He was her husband. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:32.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,-那个自杀了的女的  -你怎么发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- The woman who killed herself. - How'd you find that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:35.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是那个电脑屏保上的男的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's the guy on the screensaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个意外转折\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I like that twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:41.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,-或许他生病了  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Maybe he got sick. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,她和另一个人知道他命不久矣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She and the other fellow knew he was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:47.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,他多苟延残喘一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every day he lingered on was another day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,就要多蚕食一天他们所需要的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was consuming food they needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们帮他脱离苦海\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So they put him out of his misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:53.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,一枪爆头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shot to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:57.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,她牺牲了他  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She sacrificed him, Melanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:00.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像你牺牲了我一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like you did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:08.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,她做的决定是正确的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She made the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:12.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:16.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,不然她还能怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What else could she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:25.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们有上千个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's thousands of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:28.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,大门需要增援\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need reinforcements at the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:29.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈维在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where's Javi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,在发动机房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:35.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么知道发车时间的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did they find out departure time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:39.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经零下45了  而且随时会更冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's 45 below and getting colder by the minute, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.41,0:23:41.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们还会去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where else are they gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:45.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是我工程师卡维尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Engineer Cavill again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:47.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我家人乘坐的列车到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has the transport with my family arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:50.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们一上车就立刻通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need to know the moment they're on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,列车后方是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell's going on downtrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:54.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,-等等  -我和你们说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Wait. - I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:56.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,-能帮我把车尾指挥官找来吗  -你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Can you get me Tail Command? - Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:58.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,-加强戒备  -等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- More security! - Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:00.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在驶出车站之前就要被人攻占了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're about to be overrun before we leave the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.18,0:24:03.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,-已接通格雷指挥官  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Commander Grey's on the line. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:05.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗  {\u1}《血涌雷鸣》{\u}再现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that you, old Blood and Thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:05.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fn微软雅黑\fs18\b0\pos(376.9,219.5)}美国作家汉普顿·塞兹的一本纪实小说\N故事聚焦19世纪美国西部的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:07.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,外面到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the story back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:09.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,防线还能守住  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The perimeter fence is holding, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:10.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是人越来越多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but more just keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:12.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们发射了实弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We fired live rounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.06,0:24:13.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是坚守不了太久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it won't hold much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:16.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们攻破防线  炮火全开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If they break through... you unleash hell on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:19.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,竭尽全力不让他们进入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You do whatever it takes to hold them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.49,0:24:20.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,-明白吗  -是的  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is that clear? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:22.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,采取一切必要的武力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All necessary force.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,各位  最后一辆开往克拉克斯维尔市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Last train to Clarksville, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.87,0:24:27.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我家人还没上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My family isn't on board yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.75,0:24:29.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们还需要三十分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we still need 30 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.25,0:24:31.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,才能完成引擎循环\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to finish cycling up the engine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.59,0:24:36.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,这人是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.93,0:24:43.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们是科学家  我们有车票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're scientists! We have tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.86,0:25:02.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你是真的  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You're real. - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.70,0:25:04.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  梅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Way to go, Mel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.99,0:25:07.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道一个烹饪这只母老鼠的好食谱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know a great recipe for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.08,0:25:09.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,公的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:13.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有个更好的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.69,0:26:57.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Frickin' amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.24,0:27:06.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个地热出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a geothermal vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.49,0:27:13.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些暖气让老鼠活下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The warmth kept them alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.20,0:27:15.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,那条裂缝看起来像又多了一条新的裂缝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That fissure looks like it has a fresh crack in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.67,0:27:18.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是在大冰封的时候裂开的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Must have opened up in the Freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.96,0:27:20.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I bet you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.67,0:27:23.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,看来老鼠跟着人一起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess the rats came with the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.09,0:27:25.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是它们先找到了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they found it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.30,0:27:27.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后你找到了它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But then you found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.93,0:27:31.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,简直是奇迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.47,0:27:34.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,是生命  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's life, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:51.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.01,0:27:55.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,在蒸汽孔里躲藏并繁衍了七年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Seven years hiding and procreating in a steam vent,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.93,0:27:57.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在进了我们的肚子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and now straight into our stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.09,0:27:59.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.00,0:28:01.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,毫不后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}zero regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.26,0:28:03.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在幸存几率大多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I like your chances better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.97,0:28:06.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,蒸汽孔可以给你补充热量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The vent can supplement your heat
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.43,0:28:08.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,让数据库有更多电力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and allow more power for your databases.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.39,0:28:10.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在竭尽全力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doing everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.31,0:28:14.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过我们之间还是有很长距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Still a lot of track between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.06,0:28:19.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,要是没有雪橇你要怎么来见我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What will you do without your sled to meet us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.32,0:28:20.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会走回轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll walk back to the track...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.15,0:28:26.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,带上电池和硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}pack a battery and the hard drive on the sled.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.61,0:28:28.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,有必要的话我可以往返一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could make it there and back if I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.34,0:28:42.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.05,0:28:44.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在好想明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I understand now...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.22,0:28:49.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你当初为什么要把我留在芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why you had to leave me in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.23,0:29:02.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的指令是什么  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are your orders, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.74,0:29:06.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们说他们有票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They say they're ticketed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.82,0:29:07.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们有芯片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They've got chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:10.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我的遗传学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They are my geneticists.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:12.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你答应要让他们上车的  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You agreed to have them on board, ... - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.79,0:29:13.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.87,0:29:15.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我答应你可以请六个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I agreed you could have six.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.96,0:29:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们需要六个守卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right now we need six Jacks more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.08,0:29:20.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有他们我不走  约瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am not going without all of them, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.54,0:29:22.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  我们没空争了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know what? We don't have time to discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.88,0:29:24.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,让所有人上车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's just get everyone on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.17,0:29:27.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.73,0:29:29.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.65,0:29:31.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,干掉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Terminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.31,0:29:41.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,永远别忘了  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Never forget, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.02,0:29:44.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,列车要听我指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The train runs on my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.57,0:29:48.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,预计出发时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Estimated time of departure?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.95,0:29:52.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,-28分钟  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- 28 minutes. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:53.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要去后车了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now I'm going downtrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.12,0:29:56.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在主门也开火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we're going to open fire on the main gate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.83,0:29:59.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你只管完成循环\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just finish the damn cycle-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.63,0:30:02.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备好出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and be ready to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.29,0:30:03.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,会准备好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:05.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:08.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们坐吉普车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll take the Jeep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.17,0:30:45.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.05,0:30:53.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,砰砰声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ping.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:31:58.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,你今天可是够精彩啊  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're having quite the day, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.37,0:32:01.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在你失去了气球数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now you've lost your balloon data.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.08,0:32:05.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,部不不不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.58,0:32:06.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I bet you're feeling a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.63,0:32:08.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟雪里的那女人感同身受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like our friend out in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.09,0:32:10.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的  那个...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, the woman who, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.92,0:32:12.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.63,0:32:15.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,以那样的方式自杀  我逐渐有了尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Suicide in that manner, I've--I've grown to respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.97,0:32:19.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然取决于周遭状况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}depending on the circumstances, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.26,0:32:21.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,有时候  它会变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes it--it transforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.60,0:32:24.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在说些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.27,0:32:26.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不会明白的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.23,0:32:27.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我对她毫无尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've no respect for her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.02,0:32:29.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,她抛下了她的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She left her child behind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.69,0:32:32.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,她那么做是为了和她的孩子在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She did it to be with her child,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.57,0:32:36.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为她以为他们会团聚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because she thought that they would be reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.20,0:32:37.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,多愁善感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sentimentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.32,0:32:40.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,就跟她无法吃她丈夫的理由一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Same reason she couldn't eat her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.83,0:32:43.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了什么  她的任务失败\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And for what? Her mission failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.16,0:32:46.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,她牺牲了她的家庭  她的人性  一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She sacrificed her family, her humanity, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.46,0:32:48.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,就跟你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.21,0:32:51.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个任务还没完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This mission is not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.96,0:32:54.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉克斯会在冷锁处见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alex is meeting me at the cold lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.97,0:32:57.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  回到艾莉克斯身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, yes. Get back to Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.51,0:32:59.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,把她从魔鬼身边救走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Save her from the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.76,0:33:02.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会再抓一只老鼠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll catch another rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:05.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会再坚持两周  混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll make it two more weeks, you sack of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.06,0:33:08.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这很有说服力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I find it telling, this notion
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.77,0:33:12.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你比我优秀的观念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you're such a better human than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.65,0:33:16.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我救了你抛下的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saved the daughter you left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.28,0:33:22.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许你该感激我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps a-a little gratitude is in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.05,0:34:21.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该跟四个警卫在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They should be with four bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.72,0:34:22.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的家...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My par--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:24.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我家长是老人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my parents are elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.02,0:34:28.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,立刻放下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Drop those, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.89,0:34:32.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我女儿八岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, my--my daughter is eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.40,0:34:34.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们没登记  我需要你去找他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If they're not checked in, I need you to look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.82,0:34:39.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,喂  喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.99,0:34:44.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该还没到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think they're here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.49,0:34:48.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,火车头  回话  火车头  回话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Engine, come in. Engine, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.25,0:34:51.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,火车头  回话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Engine, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.25,0:34:54.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是火车头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.38,0:34:55.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我失去了跟格雷指挥官的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've lost contact with Commander Grey.
